Dar es Salaam. The Vice President s Office (VPO) has refuted reports which went viral on social media that Ms Samiah Suluhu Hassan has requested to stand down from her post. A statement sent to the media said the Vice President will continue to assist President John Magufuli in serving wananchi. The reports which went viral on social media aren t true; those who fabricated them want to create tension among wananchi, read part of the report. The VPO urged wananchi to ignore the seditious reports. 